<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وتعرف الأولى بوزن <span class="c1">"حبلى"</span> ... و<span class="c1">"مرطى"</span> و<span class="c1">"شعبى"</span> و<span class="c1">"فعلى"</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>مقابلا <span class="c2">(٢)</span> <span class="c1">"فعلان"</span> أو مبين <span class="c2">(٣)</span> ما<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>يبين بـ<span class="c1">"الدعوى"</span> و<span class="c1">"صرعى"</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
